  <para style="s">Salutation</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Συμεὼν<note caller="1" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Συμεών </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A 33 307 436 442 642 1175 1448 1735 1739 1852 2344 <char style="it">Byz</char><char style="add">pt</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> arm geo ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">Σίμων </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B Ψ 5 81 1243 1611 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char><char style="add">pt</char> <char style="it">l</char> 147 <char style="it">l</char> 590 <char style="it">l</char> 592 <char style="it">l</char> 603 <char style="it">l</char> 680 <char style="it">l</char> 1364 <char style="it">l</char><char style="add">AD</char> it<char style="add">ar, z</char> vg cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> eth slav BTI DHH?</char></note> Πέτρος δοῦλος καὶ ἀπόστολος Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ τοῖς ἰσότιμον ἡμῖν λαχοῦσιν πίστιν ἐν δικαιοσύνῃ τοῦ θεοῦ ἡμῶν καὶ σωτῆρος Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ, <verse number="2" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1.2 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">χάρις … πληθυνθείη </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:2">Jd 2</ref></char></note>χάρις ὑμῖν καὶ εἰρήνη πληθυνθείη ἐν ἐπιγνώσει τοῦ θεοῦ καὶ Ἰησοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν<note caller="2" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ καὶ Ἰησοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">B C 1448 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K] <char style="it">l</char> 883 <char style="it">l</char> 884 <char style="it">l</char> 1159 ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ καὶ Χριστοῦ Ἰησοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">5 33 81 436 642 2344 <char style="it">l</char> 598 <char style="it">l</char> 1365 it<char style="add">q</char> vg<char style="add">cl</char> vg<char style="add">mss</char> ? Augustine ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ καὶ Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A L 307 1735 1739 2492 <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 592 <char style="it">add</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">κυρίου </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">after</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">καί </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">too;</char> <char style="it">l</char> 921 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">καὶ κυρίου Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) vg<char style="add">mss</char>? syr<char style="add">pal</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm (eth) (slav) ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ καὶ σωτῆρος Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(<char style="it">see</char> <char style="xt"><ref loc="2PE 1:1">1.1</ref>)</char> 442 <char style="it">l</char> 596 ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ Ἰησοῦ τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1611 it<char style="add">ar</char> syr<char style="add">ph, h</char> cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">ms</char></char> geo Speculum ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1243 <char style="it">l</char> 422 ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">P Ψ 1175 1852 it<char style="add">z</char> vg<char style="add">ww, st</char> (cop<char style="add">sa</char>) BJ</char></note>.</para>
  <para style="s">The Christian’s Call and Election</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1.3 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">τοῦ … ἀρετῇ </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 2:9">1 Pe 2.9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ὡς πάντα ἡμῖν τῆς θείας δυνάμεως αὐτοῦ τὰ πρὸς ζωὴν καὶ εὐσέβειαν δεδωρημένης διὰ τῆς ἐπιγνώσεως τοῦ καλέσαντος ἡμᾶς ἰδίᾳ δόξῃ καὶ ἀρετῇ<note caller="3" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἰδίᾳ δόξῃ καὶ ἀρετῇ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A C P Ψ 33 81 307 436 442 1243 1735 1739 1852 2344 <char style="it">l</char> 596 <char style="it">l</char> 884 it<char style="add">ar, h, q</char> vg syr<char style="add">ph, h, pal</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char> arm eth geo (slav) Didymus; (Speculum) ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">διὰ δόξης καὶ ἀρετῆς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B 5 642 1175 1448 1611 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L] <char style="it">Lect</char> (it<char style="add">z</char>)</char></note> <verse number="4" style="v" />δι᾽ ὧν τὰ τίμια καὶ μέγιστα ἡμῖν ἐπαγγέλματα<char style="add">♦</char> δεδώρηται, ἵνα διὰ τούτων γένησθε θείας κοινωνοὶ φύσεως ἀποφυγόντες τῆς ἐν τῷ κόσμῳ ἐν ἐπιθυμίᾳ φθορᾶς<note caller="4" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.4 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τῆς ἐν τῷ κόσμῳ ἐν ἐπιθυμίᾳ φθορᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">A B it<char style="add">ar, h, z</char> ? vg? Speculum ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">♦ τῆς ἐν κόσμῳ ἐν ἐπιθυμίᾳ φθορᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">307 436 442 642 1448 1735 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L (P)] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 592 <char style="it">l</char> 598 <char style="it">l</char> 1154 <char style="it">omit</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) it<char style="add">ar, h, z</char> ? vg? ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τῆς ἐν κόσμῳ ἐπιθυμίας φθορᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">33<char style="add">vid</char> 81 cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">mss</char>, bo, v<char style="add">vid</char></char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τῆς ἐν κόσμῳ ἐπιθυμίας καὶ φθορᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">C Ψ 5 (81 <char style="it">omit</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">καί</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1175 1243 (1611 1852 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τῷ κόσμῳ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1739 syr<char style="add">h, pal</char> arm geo slav ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τὴν ἐν τῷ κόσμῳ ἐπιθυμίαν φθορᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(𝔓<char style="add">72</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">φθοράν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) ℵ (eth) Jerome EU LB BJ</char></note><char style="add">♦</char>. <verse number="5" style="v" />καὶ αὐτὸ τοῦτο δὲ<char style="add">♦</char> σπουδὴν πᾶσαν παρεισενέγκαντες ἐπιχορηγήσατε ἐν τῇ πίστει ὑμῶν τὴν ἀρετήν, ἐν δὲ τῇ ἀρετῇ τὴν γνῶσιν, <verse number="6" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1.6‑7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:22-23">Ga 5.22‑23</ref></char></note>ἐν δὲ τῇ γνώσει τὴν ἐγκράτειαν, ἐν δὲ τῇ ἐγκρατείᾳ τὴν ὑπομονήν, ἐν δὲ τῇ ὑπομονῇ τὴν εὐσέβειαν, <verse number="7" style="v" />ἐν δὲ τῇ εὐσεβείᾳ τὴν φιλαδελφίαν, ἐν δὲ τῇ φιλαδελφίᾳ τὴν ἀγάπην. <verse number="8" style="v" />ταῦτα γὰρ ὑμῖν ὑπάρχοντα καὶ πλεονάζοντα οὐκ ἀργοὺς οὐδὲ ἀκάρπους καθίστησιν εἰς τὴν τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ ἐπίγνωσιν· <verse number="9" style="v" />ᾧ γὰρ μὴ πάρεστιν ταῦτα, τυφλός ἐστιν μυωπάζων λήθην λαβὼν τοῦ καθαρισμοῦ τῶν πάλαι αὐτοῦ ἁμαρτιῶν<char style="add">♦</char>. <verse number="10" style="v" />διὸ μᾶλλον, ἀδελφοί, σπουδάσατε βεβαίαν<note caller="5" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε βεβαίαν … ποιεῖσθαι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B C 642 1448 1739 (2344 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ποιεῖσθε</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> Ambrose ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε ἵνα διὰ τῶν καλῶν ἔργων βεβαίαν … ποιῆσθε </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(<char style="it">or by itacism</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ποιεῖσθε</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) ℵ (A </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑμῶν ἔργων</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) Ψ 5 81 307 436 (1175) 1611 (1735 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἔργων ὑμῶν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1852 <char style="it">l</char> 60 <char style="it">l</char> 1365<char style="add">1/2</char> it<char style="add">ar, (t), z</char> (vg) syr<char style="add">(ph), (h), pal</char> (cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char>) arm<char style="add">mss</char> (eth) geo (slav<char style="add">mss</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἔργων ὑμῶν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε διὰ τῶν καλῶν ἔργων βεβαίαν … ποιεῖσθαι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">442 <char style="it">l</char> 596 arm<char style="add">mss</char> slav<char style="add">mss</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε βεβαίαν εἰ ὑμῶν τὴν ἐκλογὴν ποιεῖσθε </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1243</char></note> ὑμῶν τὴν κλῆσιν καὶ ἐκλογὴν ποιεῖσθαι<note caller="5" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε βεβαίαν … ποιεῖσθαι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B C 642 1448 1739 (2344 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ποιεῖσθε</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> Ambrose ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε ἵνα διὰ τῶν καλῶν ἔργων βεβαίαν … ποιῆσθε </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(<char style="it">or by itacism</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ποιεῖσθε</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) ℵ (A </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑμῶν ἔργων</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) Ψ 5 81 307 436 (1175) 1611 (1735 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἔργων ὑμῶν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 1852 <char style="it">l</char> 60 <char style="it">l</char> 1365<char style="add">1/2</char> it<char style="add">ar, (t), z</char> (vg) syr<char style="add">(ph), (h), pal</char> (cop<char style="add">sa, bo</char>) arm<char style="add">mss</char> (eth) geo (slav<char style="add">mss</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἔργων ὑμῶν</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε διὰ τῶν καλῶν ἔργων βεβαίαν … ποιεῖσθαι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">442 <char style="it">l</char> 596 arm<char style="add">mss</char> slav<char style="add">mss</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σπουδάσατε βεβαίαν εἶ ὑμῶν τὴν ἐκλογὴν ποιεῖσθε </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1243</char></note>· ταῦτα γὰρ ποιοῦντες οὐ μὴ πταίσητέ ποτε. <verse number="11" style="v" />οὕτως γὰρ πλουσίως ἐπιχορηγηθήσεται ὑμῖν ἡ εἴσοδος εἰς τὴν αἰώνιον βασιλείαν τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν καὶ σωτῆρος Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1.12 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">μελλήσω … εἰδότας </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:5">Jd 5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Διὸ μελλήσω ἀεὶ ὑμᾶς ὑπομιμνῄσκειν περὶ τούτων καίπερ εἰδότας καὶ ἐστηριγμένους ἐν τῇ παρούσῃ ἀληθείᾳ. <verse number="13" style="v" />δίκαιον δὲ ἡγοῦμαι, ἐφ᾽ ὅσον εἰμὶ ἐν τούτῳ τῷ σκηνώματι, διεγείρειν ὑμᾶς ἐν ὑπομνήσει <verse number="14" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1.14 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἡ ἀπόθεσις … μου </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 5:1">2 Cor 5.1</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">καθὼς … ἐδήλωσέν μοι </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 21:18-19">Jn 21.18‑19</ref></char></note>εἰδὼς ὅτι ταχινή ἐστιν ἡ ἀπόθεσις τοῦ σκηνώματός μου, καθὼς καὶ ὁ κύριος ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦς Χριστὸς ἐδήλωσέν μοι. <verse number="15" style="v" />σπουδάσω δὲ καὶ ἑκάστοτε ἔχειν ὑμᾶς μετὰ τὴν ἐμὴν ἔξοδον τὴν τούτων μνήμην ποιεῖσθαι.</para>
  <para style="s">Christ’s Glory and the Prophetic Word</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" />Οὐ γὰρ σεσοφισμένοις μύθοις ἐξακολουθήσαντες ἐγνωρίσαμεν ὑμῖν τὴν τοῦ κυρίου ἡμῶν Ἰησοῦ Χριστοῦ δύναμιν καὶ παρουσίαν ἀλλ᾽ ἐπόπται γενηθέντες τῆς ἐκείνου μεγαλειότητος. <verse number="17" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1.17‑18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 17:1-5">Mt 17.1‑5</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 9:2-7">Mk 9.2‑7</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 9:28-35">Lk 9.28‑35</ref></char></note>λαβὼν γὰρ παρὰ θεοῦ πατρὸς τιμὴν καὶ δόξαν φωνῆς ἐνεχθείσης αὐτῷ τοιᾶσδε ὑπὸ τῆς μεγαλοπρεποῦς δόξης, Ὁ υἱός μου ὁ ἀγαπητός μου οὗτός ἐστιν<note caller="6" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὁ υἱός μου ὁ ἀγαπητός μου οὗτός ἐστιν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">οὗτός ἐστιν ὁ υἱός μου ὁ ἀγαπητός </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(<char style="it">see</char> <char style="xt"><ref loc="MAT 3:17">Mt 3.17</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 17:5">17.5</ref>)</char> ℵ A C<char style="add">1</char> Ψ 5 33 81 307 436 442 642 1243 1448 1611 1735 1739 1852 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">ar, h, z</char> vg syr<char style="add">ph, h</char> (arm geo <char style="it">omit second</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὁ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) slav Augustine EU LB BJ? TOB BTI? ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">οὗτός ἐστιν ὁ υἱός μου ὁ ἀγαπητὸς οὗτός ἐστιν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(C<char style="add">*vid</char> <char style="it">omit</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὁ ἀγαπητός</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) P 1175 cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">mss</char>, bo</char></char></note> εἰς ὃν ἐγὼ εὐδόκησα, <verse number="18" style="v" />καὶ ταύτην τὴν φωνὴν ἡμεῖς ἠκούσαμεν ἐξ οὐρανοῦ ἐνεχθεῖσαν σὺν αὐτῷ ὄντες ἐν τῷ ἁγίῳ ὄρει. <verse number="19" style="v" />καὶ ἔχομεν βεβαιότερον τὸν προφητικὸν λόγον ᾧ καλῶς ποιεῖτε προσέχοντες ὡς λύχνῳ φαίνοντι ἐν αὐχμηρῷ τόπῳ, ἕως οὗ ἡμέρα διαυγάσῃ καὶ φωσφόρος ἀνατείλῃ ἐν ταῖς καρδίαις ὑμῶν, <verse number="20" style="v" />τοῦτο πρῶτον γινώσκοντες ὅτι πᾶσα προφητεία γραφῆς ἰδίας ἐπιλύσεως οὐ γίνεται· <verse number="21" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1.21 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὑπὸ … ἄνθρωποι </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:16">2 Tm 3.16</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:11">1 Pe 1.11</ref></char></note>οὐ γὰρ θελήματι ἀνθρώπου ἠνέχθη προφητεία ποτέ<char style="add">♦</char>, ἀλλ᾽ ὑπὸ πνεύματος ἁγίου φερόμενοι ἐλάλησαν ἀπὸ θεοῦ<note caller="7" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἀπὸ θεοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> B P 442 1175 1243 1739 1852 2492 <char style="it">l</char> 596 (vg<char style="add">ms</char>) syr<char style="add">h</char> arm Augustine<char style="add">3/4</char> Quodvultdeus Varimadum ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἀπὸ θεοῦ ἅγιοι </char><char style="ft" closed="false">C (81 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἅγιοι ἀπὸ θεοῦ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) eth Didymus<char style="add">dub</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἅγιοι θεοῦ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ (A </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) Ψ 5 33 307 436 642 1448 1611 1735 2344 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 422 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἄνθρωποι </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">before</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἅγιοι; </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">l</char> 592 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦ θεοῦ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) it<char style="add">ar, h, z</char> vg syr<char style="add">ph</char> (cop<char style="add">sa<char style="add">mss</char></char>) geo slav</char></note> ἄνθρωποι.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" />
  <para style="s">False Prophets and Teachers</para>
  <para style="r">(Jude 4‑13)</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2.1 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">ἐν ὑμῖν … ψευδοδιδάσκαλοι </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:11">Mt 24.11</ref> </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">τὸν … ἀρνούμενοι </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:4">Jd 4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ἐγένοντο δὲ καὶ ψευδοπροφῆται ἐν τῷ λαῷ, ὡς καὶ ἐν ὑμῖν ἔσονται ψευδοδιδάσκαλοι, οἵτινες παρεισάξουσιν αἱρέσεις ἀπωλείας καὶ τὸν ἀγοράσαντα αὐτοὺς δεσπότην ἀρνούμενοι ἐπάγοντες ἑαυτοῖς ταχινὴν ἀπώλειαν. <verse number="2" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2.2 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">δι᾽ … βλασφημηθήσεται </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 52:5">Is 52.5</ref></char></note>καὶ πολλοὶ ἐξακολουθήσουσιν αὐτῶν ταῖς ἀσελγείαις δι᾽ οὓς ἡ ὁδὸς τῆς ἀληθείας βλασφημηθήσεται, <verse number="3" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2.3 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἐν … ἐμπορεύσονται </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:18">Ro 16.18</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 2:5">1 Th 2.5</ref></char></note>καὶ ἐν πλεονεξίᾳ πλαστοῖς λόγοις ὑμᾶς ἐμπορεύσονται, οἷς τὸ κρίμα ἔκπαλαι οὐκ ἀργεῖ καὶ ἡ ἀπώλεια αὐτῶν οὐ νυστάζει<char style="add">♦</char>.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />
