      <char style="xo" closed="false">2.4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:6">Jd 6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Εἰ γὰρ ὁ θεὸς ἀγγέλων ἁμαρτησάντων οὐκ ἐφείσατο ἀλλὰ σειραῖς<note caller="1" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σειραῖς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">72</char> Ψ 5 33 307 436 442 642 1175 1243 1448 1611 1735 1739 1852 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">(ar), z</char> vg syr<char style="add">ph</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm geo slav Didymus Cyril ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σιροῖς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A B C 81 it<char style="add">h</char> vg<char style="add">ms</char> Augustine Quodvultdeus Fulgentius Cassiodorus NIV REB EU BJ TOB BTI</char></note> ζόφου ταρταρώσας παρέδωκεν εἰς κρίσιν τηρουμένους <verse number="5" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2.5 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὄγδοον … ἐφύλαξεν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 8:18">Gn 8.18</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">κατακλυσμὸν … ἐπάξας </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 3:6">2 Pe 3.6</ref></char></note>καὶ ἀρχαίου κόσμου οὐκ ἐφείσατο ἀλλ᾽ ὄγδοον Νῶε δικαιοσύνης κήρυκα ἐφύλαξεν κατακλυσμὸν κόσμῳ ἀσεβῶν ἐπάξας <verse number="6" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2.6 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">πόλεις … κατέκρινεν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 19:24">Gn 19.24</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:7">Jd 7</ref></char></note>καὶ πόλεις Σοδόμων καὶ Γομόρρας τεφρώσας καταστροφῇ κατέκρινεν<note caller="2" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">καταστροφῇ κατέκρινεν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ℵ A C<char style="add">2</char> Ψ 5 33 81 307 436 642 1448 1611 1735 2344 2492 <char style="it">Byz</char> [K L] <char style="it">Lect</char> i